title: [Calelith Villa, Garden]
description: Once cultivated, this overgrown flower garden has a beauty of its own.  Roses of yellow and white grow wild and tall, their fragrance filling the air.  White clematis climbs an old trellis along the back of the villa.  Fireflies dance about, flitting from flower to flower.
